# SprintCycle workflow (unified / 统一工作流)

Full references: `docs/SPRINT_SDD_GATES.md` · `docs/SPRINT_OPTIMIZE_WORKFLOW.md` · `docs/CURSOR_OPTIMIZATION_RULES.md`  
Entry: `/sprint` (modes below) · Skill (evolve only): `.cursor/skills/sprint-evolve/SKILL.md`

## Mode routing (模式路由)

| Mode | Triggers | Pipeline |
|------|----------|----------|
| **sdd** | 影响面 · 范围判定 · 假小需求 · 排查修复 · `/sprint sdd` | L/F grade → scope `C1…` → `docs/sdd-designs/` → principle review → implement |
| **optimize** | 重构 · DDD治理 · 删兼容 · 前后端对齐 · `/sprint optimize` | §0 SDD gates → Phase 1–6 → closure line |
| **evolve** | 进化 · 自动优化 · `/sprint evolve` | `evolve.py --report-only` → HITL ×2 → **optimize mode** → validate |

